User: lsrea  Fri Jun 21 18:05:12 PDT 2002
TkrDigi/src

Modified Files:
	TkrSimpleDigiAlg.cxx 
Log Message:
Made noise-generation parameters into Properties:
    threshold (MeV)  -- energy level to register hit (default: 0.03)
    noiseSigma (MeV) -- amount to randomly fluctuate deposited energy (def: 0.01)
    noiseOccupancy   -- fraction of strips given a noise hit (def: 1.e-4)
setting all to zero gives faithful digitization of all MC hits.
    

